表的代码预览账户

drop index account_PK on account;


alter table account
drop foreign key FK_ACCOUNT_开户_BRANCH;

drop table if exists account;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: account */
/*==============================================================*/
create table account
(
account_id varchar(50) not null comment '',
branch_name varchar(255) comment '',
balance float(8,2) comment '',
latest_visited date comment ''
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: account_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique index account_PK on account
(
account_id
);

alter table account add constraint FK_ACCOUNT_开户_BRANCH foreign key (branch_name)
references branch (branch_name) on delete restrict on update restrict;
